### Car Rental Server - API Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### ============================================
### USER APIs
### ============================================

### 1. Register User
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "phone": "1234567890"
}

### 2. Login User
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Get User Data (Protected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/data
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Get Available Cars (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/cars

### ============================================
### OWNER APIs
### ============================================

### 5. Change Role to Owner (Protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/owner/change-role
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "owner"
}

