### 7. Get Owner Cars (Protected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/owner/cars
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Toggle Car Availability (Protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/owner/toggle-car
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "carId": "your_car_id_here"
}

### 9. Delete Car (Protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/owner/delete-car
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "carId": "your_car_id_here"
}

### 10. Get Dashboard Data (Protected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/owner/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Update User Profile Image (Protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/owner/update-image
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="profile.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./path/to/your/image.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### ============================================
### BOOKING APIs
### ============================================

### 12. Check Car Availability (Public)
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings/check-availability
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "carId": "your_car_id_here",
  "startDate": "2025-12-20",
  "endDate": "2025-12-25"
}

### 13. Create Booking (Protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings/create
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "carId": "your_car_id_here",
  "startDate": "2025-12-20",
  "endDate": "2025-12-25",
  "totalPrice": 250
}

### 14. Get User Bookings (Protected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings/user
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 15. Get Owner Bookings (Protected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings/owner
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 16. Change Booking Status (Protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings/change-status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingId": "your_booking_id_here",
  "status": "confirmed"
}

